Dead-End arrives at the Stunticons starcruiser,  The Dark Avian, 
with a load of energon. "There," he says to himself, "We now have 
enough energon to do almost anything." He takes some temporary 
laser turrets from the base and comences to position them around 
th ship in hiding, "Only some intense scanning should be able to 
pick these suckers up."
